					"value": "The emperor is now an enemy under the Netherbrain's control. He serves as a central character of the last fight.\r\n\r\nThis AD plays on the Emperor's turn. Extra lines are played once for when the party mindflayer uses Karsus' Compulsion on the crown and when the players are racing to get to the opened portal."
